HEADWORD: Adjunctive
<hw>Ad*junc"tive</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>adjunctivus</ets>, fr. <ets>adjungere</ets>. See
<er>Adjunct</er>.]</ety> <def>Joining; having the quality of joining;
