==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Adjunctive
<hw>Ad*junc"tive</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that which, is
joined.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Adjunctively</ent>⟦br⟧
